claim.claim-text:
A cuff stimulation electrode (100, 304) for cervical Vagus Nerve Stimulation (VNS), comprising:
An inner cuff surface that faces a nerve (103);
at least two contacts (110) arranged on said inner cuff surface for delivering electrical stimulation, and
at least one of a tilt sensor, a kinematic sensor, and a pulsation sensor;
wherein said at least one sensor is configured to generate a signal representative of physiological parameters.
